Convenience class for building a {@link DataSource} with common implementations and properties. If HikariCP, Tomcat, Commons DBCP or Oracle UCP are on the classpath one of them will be selected (in that order with Hikari first). In the interest of a uniform interface, and so that there can be a fallback to an embedded database if one can be detected on the classpath, only a small set of common configuration properties are supported.
